Hello! I took notice the sections on meditation in this article was rather slim and void of content. To justify mentioning the practice in the first place, I aimed to contextualise and differentiate this meditation with reference to secondary (news, interviews, programs) and primary sources (books Sahaja Yogis consult). This is my first large edit, so feedback is much appreciated.
